                "Activities": "<section>\n  <h2>Finance Operational Activities</h2>\n  <ul class=\"efg-detail\">\n    <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Service\">\n      <strong itemprop=\"name\">Procurement and Purchasing</strong>\n      <span itemprop=\"description\">The Order-to-Pay (O2P) process manages supplier onboarding, purchase requests, PO approval, and invoice processing. For purchases under €25,000, the Requesting Party can submit a PO directly; for purchases above €25,000, a formal Purchase Request must be submitted to Procurement. All invoices require an approved PO unless an exception is granted by Finance.</span>\n      <a class=\"chip\" itemprop=\"url\" href=\"https://efg.coupahost.com/\">Coupa</a>\n    </li>\n    <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Service\">\n      <strong itemprop=\"name\">Expense Processing</strong>\n      <span itemprop=\"description\">Employees can submit expenses and credit card claims in Coupa. Managers are empowered to approve expenses up to 1K EUR for OPEX and 2.5K EUR for COGS. All claims require supporting evidence, such as a tax invoice, and must be submitted within 30 days.</span>\n      <a class=\"chip\" itemprop=\"url\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1H5l80yZn3CwpBuED24lzavG5HeQ6wB6Rm8u3qSeVMJU/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.16a68wwgpkbk\">SOP: Expense Processing</a>\n    </li>\n    <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Service\">\n      <strong itemprop=\"name\">Prize Money Payments</strong>\n      <span itemprop=\"description\">Prize money for B2C and B2B is managed via the Payment Labs platform. The process involves tournament operations setting up tournaments and funding requests, financial operations processing funding to the FBO account, and the Payment Approval Group submitting payments to winners.</span>\n      <a class=\"chip\" itemprop=\"url\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1v6kkLSOp4MoM7HqX0eWKShPBy87chA4T9CezsJ-EqzQ/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.xmwtp8mikz9l\">SOP: Payment Processing</a>\n    </li>\n    <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Service\">\n      <strong itemprop=\"name\">Vendor Management</strong>\n      <span itemprop=\"description\">Procurement is responsible for vendor onboarding, performance management, and audits. Onboarding includes bank information verification, tax document checks, vendor due diligence, and MSA signing.</span>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n</section>",
                "Calendar": "<section>\n<h2>Finance Division Meeting and Calendar Structure</h2>\n<p>The Finance division maintains a structured approach to communication and alignment through various recurring cadences. Please note that specific dates and times for these meetings are managed within the linked external calendar.</p>\n\n<ul class=\"efg-detail\">\n  <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Event\">\n    <strong itemprop=\"name\">Finance Townhall <span class=\"efg-pill\">Quarterly</span></strong>\n    <span itemprop=\"description\">A department-wide session for company announcements, guest speakers, and individual/team achievements.</span>\n  </li>\n  <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Event\">\n    <strong itemprop=\"name\">Leadership Pulse <span class=\"efg-pill\">Monthly</span></strong>\n    <span itemprop=\"description\">Focused on strategic alignment, escalation handling, and cascading information down to teams. Participants include L1-3 leadership.</span>\n  </li>\n  <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Event\">\n    <strong itemprop=\"name\">Initiative Sync <span class=\"efg-pill\">Monthly</span></strong>\n    <span itemprop=\"description\">An operational meeting for L3 and below to provide visibility on project progress (using the Jira board) and highlight \"wins\".</span>\n  </li>\n  <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Event\">\n    <strong itemprop=\"name\">Functional Tactical</strong>\n    <span itemprop=\"description\">Team-specific meetings led by Matt, Bassem, and Markus to align on day-to-day priorities, unblock tasks, and manage workload. Frequency is determined by the lead of the department.</span>\n  </li>\n  <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Event\">\n    <strong itemprop=\"name\">1:1s <span class=\"efg-pill\">Weekly</span></strong>\n    <span itemprop=\"description\">Managers are required to maintain weekly 1:1 meetings with their direct reports.</span>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Sourcing Business Partner Meetings</h3>\n<p>The following recurring meetings are scheduled for Sourcing Business Partners:</p>\n<ul class=\"efg-schedule\">\n  <li><span class=\"n\">Publisher Operations</span><span class=\"t\">Wed · 3:30 PM GMT</span></li>\n  <li><span class=\"n\">EWC/ENC</span><span class=\"t\">Wed · 09:00 PM GMT</span></li>\n  <li><span class=\"n\">O&O</span><span class=\"t\">Wed · 10:00 AM GMT</span></li>\n  <li><span class=\"n\">MENA Operations</span><span class=\"t\">Thu · 10:00 AM GMT</span></li>\n  <li><span class=\"n\">Enterprise Technology</span><span class=\"t\">Tue · 01:30 PM GMT</span></li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
