anking structure across the EFG Group, Manage liquidity across the EFG Group, Manage cash flow forecasting across the EFG Group, Prepare treasury reporting, bank front and mid office, foreign exchange trading, Approve payment, Own the Credit card management (virtual and corporate) policy and process, Review, set up and approval of payment files, bank statements, payment terms for large suppliers and customers, Manage working capital, Manage bank KYC and bank account confirmations.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n    <h3 itemprop=\"name\">Financial Operations</h3>\n    <ul class=\"efg-cards\">\n      <li class=\"efg-card\" itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Sivakumar Govindan</strong>\n        <span class=\"role\" itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior Manager, Financial Operations</span>\n        <span class=\"loc\" itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">India</span></span>\n        <span class=\"desc\" itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Bassem Masrouha. Responsibilities: Lead and manage a team responsible for AP, Payments, AR, billing, and collections operations within the shared service center. Act as the primary point of contact for internal stakeholders (e.g., finance, sales, operations) and external stakeholders (e.g., vendors, customers) regarding AP, Payments, AR, billing, and collections matters. Maintain key performance indicators (KPIs) to track the effectiveness and efficiency of financial operations.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n    <h3 itemprop=\"name\">Financial Reporting</h3>\n    <ul class=\"efg-cards\">\n      <li class=\"efg-card\" itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Alexander Södergren</stron